Event Data.title: Al-Iman Sunday Program
Event Data.description:
Al-Iman Sunday Program:

AlhumduLilah the registration is complete for 2021-2022 academic year. Jazakumullah khairan for your participation and support. Insha'Allah, the first day of school is Sept 12th starting at 10am. Parents who registered will receive a separate email with additional details regarding what to expect on the first day.

Jazakum Allahu Khyran,
Al-Iman Institute Administration 
phone: 512 677 9891
web: https://icrraliman.org/

Riyaad As Saliheen at Maghrib
Event Data.description:
Mondays After Magrib
On Premises and Facebook live
Join us for a weekly khatirah to learn ahadith from Imam Nawawi?s Riyadh Al-Salihin. Insha?All?h, pertinent ahadith will be selected and explained to the community. The goal is to cover topics that refresh our spirituality and teach us practical aspects of practicing our faith. The program is intended for the entire family.

Community Clinic
Event Data.description:
Wednesdays
ICRR (in collaboration with Eixsys HealthCare System) will host a community clinic every Wednesday from 7pm - 9pm. There will be no charge for the indigent, uninsured and underserved, everyone else there will be a nominal charge. This is an initiative to serve the community at large, everyone is welcome. Please schedule appointments at ehsclinic.org

data.Title: Al-Iman Sunday Program
data.Description:
As Salam Alaikum Wa Rahmatullahi Wa Barakatuhu

We hope this message finds you and your family in the best of health and Iman inshAllah.

We are looking forward to welcoming the students. We are confident that in-sha-Allah, this year will be the best one yet. Online registration for 2022-23 is now open for new and returning students. Please use the link below for the registration.

https://icrraliman.org/registration/

The deadline to register is August 27th. Classes will begin in September 2022, Inshaa Allah.
As Salam Alaikum Wa Rahmatullahi Wa Barakatuhu

Jazakum Allahu Khyran,
Al-Iman Institute Administration 
phone: 512 677 9891
web: https://icrraliman.org/
